Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.19,[Sub_Phụ],,0000,0000,0000,,I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:15.83,[Sub_Phụ],,0000,0000,0000,,Give!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.66,[Sub_Phụ],,0000,0000,0000,,Ờ ờ, give, give, give!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.22,[Black_Lagoon],,0000,0000,0000,,Give?
